Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕩秋千要這麼玩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.89,0:00:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..我覺得不太對..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了個令人懷念的夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂這個傢夥 玩蕩秋千也玩得很酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 不用客氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和她做的點心可能也有你的份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事嗎..
