Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:54.79,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,475)\fad(0,0)}我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？砂川同學呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像有事來不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:02:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就奇怪今天怎麼沒一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有這麼形影不離嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼點心大概會有多出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得之後給他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這個我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是鹹鹹蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鹹味蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:19.82,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃..好吃..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次還試著烤了星型的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶中的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生日是什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1月1日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:40.73,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:40.73,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:40.73,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}猛男 生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:40.73,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是在寒假裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可朋友們總是會跑來敲門問候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1月1日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要從現在開始加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:53.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}麻糬泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:53.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}麻糬華夫餅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:53.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}麻糬甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正月..年糕麻糬..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多用年糕做的甜點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和的生日是什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:04:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..6月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 6月15日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就要到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:19.98,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}說出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 確實是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 聽起來就像要你為我慶祝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慶祝吧 你想要什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要的 不需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的什麼都不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天你能一直..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直陪著我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 感謝你降生於世
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人 必將降生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 過生日啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？你生日應該是1月1日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:19.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}唉 畢竟這日子太好記啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也記得你的生日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9月13日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為小學時 每年生日聚會你都會邀請我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝惦記 所以說是誰生日？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 大和同學啊 什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15..哦..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她生日你打算怎麼辦？有什麼安排嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 大和她好像什麼都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:06:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像只想要我的陪伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像這樣就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想帶她到處逛逛好好幫她慶生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我一起想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:16.18,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人 必將降生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿猛 你1月就要當哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我按下電梯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽你幾歲了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有40了 不過內臟年齡是22歲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好年輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別拿這麼重的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點事沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來拿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在生你的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在待產室遇上先要生的孕婦媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還把她抱進了產房 還不是一點事沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:56.51,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}快按
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不太明白 但是好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛是嘛 我..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快要有弟弟或妹妹了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人 必將降生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.62,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}快點出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 猛男同學要當哥哥了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 恭喜你 是弟弟還是妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的媽媽..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,40了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學當哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定會成為超級棒的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是當爸爸也會成為好爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得大和也會成為好媽媽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:41.77,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}害羞害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就要走了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂他好像有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可又感覺和平時沒什麼兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂這個人很難懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那傢夥基本不會說自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 難不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂川同學是寂寞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止一直在一起玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可現在和猛男同學在一起的時間減少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能覺得寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為砂川同學最喜歡猛男同學了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 我的生日不一定要兩個人過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也邀請砂川同學來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15號 你也一起來慶祝大和的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和她猜你可能是覺得寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:07.35,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}盯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 而且15號我有事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 不是寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會說起這事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不啦 我是覺得你和平時不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為是遇上了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果阿砂遇上了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他不想說的話也不必強迫他說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會等到你主動跟我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 這是之前你排的大和同學生日的日程表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這份神似美國總統一日行程的計劃表..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？有意見儘管說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}6點 在江之島看朝陽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}7點 海邊散步 拾貝殼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}8點 電影 查查看最近在放什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}10點 遊樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}12點 午餐 去好吃的店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}1點 動物園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}2點 遠足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}3點 去飲茶店喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}4點 公園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}5點 回江之島看夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}6點 送她回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先早上6點也太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 這個計劃完全是以晴天為前提的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果下雨的話怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有休息和路上的時間沒算進去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了你 大部分人都無法完成這個日程表的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 看來要重寫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨也能去的地方有哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡如何？中學時學園祭慶功會去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樓裡好像有保齡球和卡拉OK之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就決定去那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時的你..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:34.77,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}超搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手插不進保齡球的球孔..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果拿起球就扔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有過那種事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次看到那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:49.41,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好像在扔壘球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每次扔球都會引起店裡一片騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後還吸引了不少人圍觀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你記得很清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事很難忘的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}保齡球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上六點沒開門啦 定在10點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 10點是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:59.92,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}10點 保齡球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:59.92,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}12點 午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛肉蓋飯..拉麵..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,點心種類多的地方比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟大和同學喜歡做點心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那她應該也喜歡吃喜歡看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 因為是生日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想請她吃份大餐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像可以預約
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜品種類好像也很多的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是這個 阿砂 開始預約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他還有什麼地方可去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有..水族館..天文館..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電影院..這個你也寫了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多就這麼多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文館啊 小學時去過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候 你掉進修理中的大坑裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果你自己爬出來時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被旁邊人誤以為是地底人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的記得很牢呢 腦袋好使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就去天文館
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和也喜歡星星 她一定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:11:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹勁十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因為很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫喜歡的人慶祝生日 是這麼幸福的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是和你一起去過的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 畢竟打了10年交道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 認識這麼久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說禮物呢？決定好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全給忘了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到生日就是禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般來說是啦 你有錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:41.19,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}畢竟你一直買烤肉什麼的來吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我借你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用別人的錢給大和慶祝算什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那去打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個 阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:50.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}只要時薪夠好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:50.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}肯用短期工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:50.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}肯用高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:50.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}隨便什麼工作都行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.83,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}10點 車站前集合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.83,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}保齡球（移動 公車7分鐘 走路20分鐘左右）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.83,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,\N{\an7}12點 午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.83,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}麗塔咖啡餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.83,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}進行預約
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.83,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}（告訴他們有人生日）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.83,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,\N{\an7}2點 天氣好就去公園
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.83,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}天氣不好就去咖啡廳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都調查好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要把大和生日這天變成最棒的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你也有別的地方要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要先繞去一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就回家睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 謝謝你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是有種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事就好..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 砂川同學並不是寂寞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:56.18,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日就兩個人過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:56.18,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一週
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這麼幸福真的可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 等下還要去打工的面試
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日 好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼都不需要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的只要你陪著我就很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是騙人哦 是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我去做吧 我很樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 總之我希望做短期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你這樣的人才很珍貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不嫌棄的話 請務必長期做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十感！多教！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:44.02,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}十分感謝 請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 打工搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你 在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:51.40,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}兄貴茶館
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:51.40,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}肌肉成群
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:51.40,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}主任：蘇西骨山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,..這沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這家店菜單名目很少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比較記得住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不是說這個..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次和大和一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和大和同學說了打工的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為你要給她個驚喜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..嗯 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 你願意陪我選禮物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我想起了你的送禮品味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送了你什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲子之類的..還有石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 這個如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:44.71,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}歐蕾咖啡杯&茶勺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼？茶碗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前陣子 大和同學有說過歐蕾咖啡碗很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛 我家沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想用這個喝歐蕾咖啡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 這就是所謂的歐蕾咖啡碗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:57.18,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿著就像茶杯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂對人真是觀察入微呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他對我也是非常注意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 那個送大和如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果大和戴上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該很可愛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想送這個給她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在打工費到手前被人買走就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拜託店家幫我們保留一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:28.25,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}當然可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不錯啊 相當理想 是新人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的蛋白質茶 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你去的是那個健身房？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的三角肌好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是自家練的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:56.30,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是個幸福的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:16:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽 你身子沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:04.99,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你爸說的話都一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老媽是沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我在醫院遇到阿誠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說他父親住院了 你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子不肯說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？進來如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家裡人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 媽媽和姐姐2個人去海外旅行了 不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為手機不通所以聯絡不上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個人嗎？你爸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨她說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前陣子爸爸病倒了 所以去醫院住一段？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼住一段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然要開刀 不過有親戚的叔叔幫忙看著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手術是什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..6月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人必將誕生 人終將死去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是偶然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那場手術 我也要去守著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去慶祝大和同學的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去了 我要和你一塊去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會跟大和說明理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和她一定會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別跟大和同學說我爸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是說的話 那孩子會很擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說 猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 不想妨礙朋友和女友度過的第一個生日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都期待成那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:18:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能是妨礙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你把期待已久的計劃作廢 跑來守著我爸的手術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也完全不會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸的病 很早以前就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以多少已經做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂的爸爸 是個不太引人注目的好人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫院說謝絕探病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說他心臟從以前就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你小學的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就病倒過一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時好像就很危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽 明明知情卻不跟我說麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算在一起相處了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有我所不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算知道生日是幾號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算知道內褲的花紋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也還有很多不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很多不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是阿砂..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有很多我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 現在要去醫院嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}你這什麼打扮..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 我不會辜負你的心意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不要太過擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽了這個我就有些安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽你身子沒事吧？
